import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import { Container, Typography, Box, Paper, Grid, Chip } from '@mui/material'; import api from '../services/api'; import Sidebar from './Sidebar'; export default function Reports() { const [daily, setDaily] = useState({}); const [outstanding, setOutstanding] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { api.get('/reports/daily').then(res => setDaily(res.data)); api.get('/reports/outstanding').then(res => setOutstanding(res.data)); }, []); return ( Reports Orders Today {daily.ordersToday || 0} Revenue {daily.revenueToday || 0} FCFA Pending {daily.pendingToday || 0} Low Stock Outstanding Payments Order Customer Due {outstanding.map(o => ( {o.id} {o.customer_name} ))}
); }
